Media playback is unsupported on your device In full: Lord Rose interview with Laura Kuenssberg 12 October 2015 Last updated at 12:41 BST
In full: Lord Rose interview with Laura Kuenssberg after he launched the Britain Stronger in Europe campaign for the UK to stay in the European Union in the forthcoming in-out referendum.
